<style src="./PagetitleComponent.css"></style>
<template src="./PagetitleComponent.html"></template>
<script>
    export default {
        name: "PagetitleComponent",
        props: {
            titleName: String,
            navList: Array
        },
        computed: {
            needNav() {
                return this.navList.length > 0;
            }
        }
    }
</script>
